From 2c0351faab68d5ea4af42db60f781e4ca2d2ed43 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Leo Rodarte <leorodarte07@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 14 Mar 2026 15:32:39 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 34/46] Close three fingerprint gaps: extend
 --fingerprint-screen with optional DPR (7th value), add
 --fingerprint-connection for navigator.connection spoofing, and add
 --fingerprint-media-features for CSS media query overrides (color-scheme,
 reduced-motion, contrast, forced-colors, color-gamut)

